dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Hey, wanna talk about ice hockey?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Sure! I don't know too much about it, but I'm open to learning about it!

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's a super fast-paced sport, basically two teams try to hit a puck into the other's net using sticks!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It seems like it's dangerous because the players get into fights a lot!

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Yeah, it can get pretty physical, but that's part of the game, right?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I guess, but do these players ever get seriously hurt?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sadly, yeah, injuries are pretty common, concussions and broken bones are no rarity

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I guess it's pretty fast paced and exciting, right?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Totally! It's one of the fastest team sports out there, super intense!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: How many players are on each team?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Each team's got 6 players on the ice at a time!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Does that include the goalie?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: The goalie's one of the 6, plus 5 other skaters!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: They all seem to skate so flawlessly!  It must become second nature to them.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Yeah, they're super skilled, skating's like walking to them!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Do ice hockey players typically start playing at a young age?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Most pros start skating and playing hockey when they're just kids!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I figured they must, since they're so good at it!

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: It's crazy how good they get with all that practice and training from a young age!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Is it a popular sport in college?

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Yeah, it's pretty big in colleges, especially in the US and Canada!
